{"tid":1361081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重開) [投訴撚出動] 睇緊 ch85 傑志對曼城嘅全部同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-24T13:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:02:07.000Z","uid":83543,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"093ba78fe68642a70a60319bfb172714c80758b8","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"波台無人理, 時事台開過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無理由21分鐘無咗聲! <br />\n又係時候搞搞佢<br />\n<br />\n攻撃方向:<br />\n《電視通用業務守則 &mdash; 節目標準》<br />\n第9章 第3條 有關持平的一般準則<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/policies_regulations/cop/code_tvprog_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fcommon%2Fpolicies_regulations%2Fcop%2Fcode_tvprog_c.pdf&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0A8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=9b8c50ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/policies_regulations/cop/code_tvprog_c.pdf</a><br />\n由於呢個喺比賽節目, 而且唱歌係可以影響到各方球員嘅, 所以絕對可以攞嚟做武器<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投訴表格在此:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0A8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=0f5a55bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n節目名:<br />\n賽馬會傑志中心盃: 傑志 對 曼城<br />\n<br />\n播映時間: 20:21<br />\n<br />\n<ins>揀頻道嗰到, 揀完 ch85 要撳新增</ins><br />\n<br />\n投訴事項:<br />\n此比賽節目刻意迴避於香港大球場於 20:21 所發生的事件。在20:21，比賽踏入21分鐘時，此比賽節目的現場聲音明顯被降低。無綫電視的行為使觀眾不能準確地了解於香港大球場發生的事件。此舉違犯《電視通用業務守則 &mdash; 節目標準》第9章 第3條 有關持平的一般準則中，不應隱瞞事實並誤導觀眾的行為。<br />\n<br />\n(想投訴鍾仔嘅, 自己再寫)<br />\n<br />\n當 TVB 犯錯事, 相關嘅新聞節目如 新聞、時事節目、財經節目、個人意見節目、紀錄片、採用調查手法報道的節目、兒童教育節目、以醫療及健康為題材的節目、比賽節目 都可以用呢條入佢. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油<br />\n沒有暴動只有暴政</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd44c069d69360be51d0ea184b272284cfbb31d6","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:43:53.000Z","msg":"727入元朗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7136688db5b4aa2fd41c36bfebb483f934f207f9","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"撤回逃犯條例修訂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30be568df302eee1192202c9f240dce32b482167","tid":1361081,"uid":101110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"香港人一定要學識投訴<br />\n唔係口講<br />\n係要sd email<br />\n你想寄信都得"},{"pid":"38bdbb5e1d82202ec78c837df6acd00c7289b38a","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:47:02.000Z","msg":"撤回暴動定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191347e7a48b0993478258d41052a2648b670e40","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"成立獨立調查委員會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84659f1ac7599265fbacc1aa163ef9d76c94f0e","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"官員問責下台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8b67bfd639bb47157edd09e3b296047ab67a67","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"衝落場唔影可以加落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43c9252d60f623fbb2cf29446560fc432fe6c3c","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"調查721元朗恐襲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849ebccca633fdabde088bce4a9fce9df7e422b5","tid":1361081,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"衝入場喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}